Well It is also an O(n) solution so why it is causing TLE problem 
- right the simple reason for it is ```redundant search``` or you can say checks 

### okay then how we gonna make it more optimized 
- No problem by simple analysis the whole point is ```node+1``` or ```node-1``` it matters and ```duplicate``` matters but here we only have to take look when it reached out ```n-1``` last index thats the point 
- so by considering it you can already make it vis at once 
- and also clear the list of duplicates to ```prevent redundant search``` thats all optimization it will takes 

