# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
The approach is very simple, calculate the frequency of the characters and return **half the sum of the frequency difference between s and t.**

# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(N)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity:O(26)
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

