With first for loap count the frequency of character's in "S" string.
With second loap if frequency if character present in S then decrement it, otherwise increment the required character.
The code is self explict. 
```
class Solution {
    public int minSteps(String s, String t) {
       int sCount[]=new int[26];
       int sRequired=0;
       for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++)sCount[s.charAt(i)-'a']++;

        for(int i=0;i<t.length();i++){
            int no=t.charAt(i)-'a';
            if(sCount[no]>0)sCount[no]--;
            else sRequired++;
            }
        return sRequired;  
    }
}
```

